snippet.title: Khaleej Times
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official YouTube channel of Khaleej Times, UAE's first and longest-running English daily. 
Interested in all the news and events from the UAE with a global perspective? No one covers it like us. 

Subscribe to the YouTube channel of UAE's #1 News website for exclusive behind-the-scene videos, original content and more. 

Visit us at www.khaleejtimes.com. 
Follow us on Facebook at facebook.com/khaleejtimes, 
Twitter at @khaleejtimes
Telegram at https://t.me/KhaleejTimes
